text: Novoakkulayevo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Kurmankeyevsky Selsoviet, Davlekanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 195 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 12 km from Davlekanovo, 4 km from Dyuryuli. == References == Category:Rural localities in Davlekanovsky District
title: Novoakkulayevo
